de.oaam.model.oaam.allocations

Interface AllocationsContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Allocations, Suballocations
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AllocationsContainerAImpl, AllocationsImpl, SuballocationsImpl

    public interface AllocationsContainerA
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. The root element of the allocations model.

    The following features are supported:

    • Device Assignments
    • Subdevice Assignments
    • Connection Assignments
    • Task Assignments
    • Signal Assignments
    • Suballocations
    • Subconnection Assignments
    See Also:
    AllocationsPackage.getAllocationsContainerA()
